CPPCC Vice-Chairman Meet HK Business Tycoon
BEIJING , November 30 ( Xinhua ) -- Wang Zhaoguo , vice-chairman of the National Committee of the Chinese People 's Political Consultative Conference ( CPPCC ) , met here today with Choi Koon-shun , president of the Hong Kong Sun Wah Group .
Choi , who is also a member of the CPPCC National Committee , came here to donate one million yuan ( about 120,000 U.S. dollars ) to Wuling University that locates in Zhangjiajie City , Hunan Province in central China .
His donation will be used for an education fund to award outstanding teachers and students .
Wang , who is also head of the United Front Work Department of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China , said the education development is essential to the overall quality of the Chinese nation , and he hopes people in all social sectors will offer support to China 's education .
